title: Delhi's iconic 'Kake Da Dhaba' in soup after video of man 'kneading dough with feet' surfaces: Must Watch
text:
Follow @ZeeNews 
New Delhi: A video allegedly showing a man 'kneading dough with his feet' at Delhi's iconic 'Kake Da Hotel' has gone viral since it was uploaded on social media. Several versions of the clip have popped up on Facebook and Twitter. 
However, the restaurant insists the man was washing clothes and had nothing to do with cooking.
